# fin-loans-contract-processor — REST Client (VS Code)
# Extensão necessária: "REST Client" por Huachao Mao (humao.rest-client)
#
# Fluxo básico:
#   1. make up                     → sobe os serviços
#   2. make seed                   → cria o produto dev com api_key fixa
#   3. Dispare o request de auth   → token capturado automaticamente
#   4. Submeta um contrato         → pegue o id na resposta para consultar depois
#
# Se não quiser rodar o seed, crie um produto pelo request "Criar produto" e
# cole a api_key retornada em @apiKey abaixo.

@baseUrl    = http://localhost:8000
@apiVersion = /api/v1

# api_key padrão do seed — troque se criou o produto na mão
@apiKey = dev-api-key-12345


# =============================================================================
# AUTH
# =============================================================================

### Gerar token JWT
# @name auth
POST {{baseUrl}}{{apiVersion}}/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "api_key": "{{apiKey}}"
}

# O token fica em {{auth.response.body.access_token}} e é reutilizado abaixo.


# =============================================================================
# PRODUTOS
# =============================================================================

### Criar produto (pule se já rodou o seed)
# @name createProduct
POST {{baseUrl}}{{apiVersion}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Dev Product",
  "slug": "dev-product"
}

# A api_key aparece uma única vez nessa resposta — copie e cole em @apiKey acima.


### Listar produtos (pegar o product_id)
# @name listProducts
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiVersion}}/products


# =============================================================================
# CONTRATOS
# =============================================================================
# @idempotencyKey fixo abaixo → mesmo contrato a cada reenvio.
# Para testar idempotência: dispare o request "Submeter contrato" duas vezes
# com a mesma key — a resposta é idêntica e nada é reprocessado.
# Para criar um novo contrato: troque a key por outro UUID.

@idempotencyKey = a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890

# product_id do seed. Se criou manualmente, copie de listProducts.response.body.items[0].id
@productId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001


### Submeter contrato
# @name submitContract
POST {{baseUrl}}{{apiVersion}}/contracts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth.response.body.access_token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{idempotencyKey}}

{
  "product_id": "{{productId}}",
  "cpf": "529.982.247-25",
  "name": "João da Silva",
  "email": "joao.silva@example.com",
  "phone": "11987654321",
  "amount_cents": 1500000,
  "interest_rate": 0.0199,
  "installments": 12,
  "disbursement_date": "2026-09-01",
  "external_reference": "REF-DEV-001"
}


### Consultar contrato (usa o id retornado pelo POST acima)
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiVersion}}/contracts/{{submitContract.response.body.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth.response.body.access_token}}


### Submeter contrato com UUID novo (cria um contrato diferente a cada envio)
POST {{baseUrl}}{{apiVersion}}/contracts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth.response.body.access_token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}

{
  "product_id": "{{productId}}",
  "cpf": "529.982.247-25",
  "name": "João da Silva",
  "email": "joao.silva@example.com",
  "phone": "11987654321",
  "amount_cents": 2000000,
  "interest_rate": 0.0249,
  "installments": 24,
  "disbursement_date": "2026-09-15",
  "external_reference": "REF-DEV-002"
}


# =============================================================================
# CENÁRIOS DE ERRO
# =============================================================================

### CPF inválido → 422
POST {{baseUrl}}{{apiVersion}}/contracts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth.response.body.access_token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}

{
  "product_id": "{{productId}}",
  "cpf": "111.111.111-11",
  "name": "Teste CPF Inválido",
  "amount_cents": 500000,
  "interest_rate": 0.015,
  "installments": 6,
  "disbursement_date": "2026-09-01"
}


### Data de desembolso no passado → 422
POST {{baseUrl}}{{apiVersion}}/contracts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth.response.body.access_token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}

{
  "product_id": "{{productId}}",
  "cpf": "529.982.247-25",
  "name": "Teste Data Passada",
  "amount_cents": 500000,
  "interest_rate": 0.015,
  "installments": 6,
  "disbursement_date": "2020-01-01"
}


### Sem Idempotency-Key → 422
POST {{baseUrl}}{{apiVersion}}/contracts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth.response.body.access_token}}

{
  "product_id": "{{productId}}",
  "cpf": "529.982.247-25",
  "name": "Teste Sem Key",
  "amount_cents": 500000,
  "interest_rate": 0.015,
  "installments": 6,
  "disbursement_date": "2026-09-01"
}


### Sem token → 401
POST {{baseUrl}}{{apiVersion}}/contracts
Content-Type: application/json
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}

{
  "product_id": "{{productId}}",
  "cpf": "529.982.247-25",
  "name": "Teste Sem Auth",
  "amount_cents": 500000,
  "interest_rate": 0.015,
  "installments": 6,
  "disbursement_date": "2026-09-01"
}


### Contrato inexistente → 404
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiVersion}}/contracts/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{auth.response.body.access_token}}


# =============================================================================
# HEALTH
# =============================================================================

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiVersion}}/health
